"}|ThemeStoreDescription~

Ultra Store (or more appropriately ULTRA STOOORREE!) is perfect for a lot of different store types, especially those with a large catalog. Ultra Store has a big category navigation, shop by brand, shop by attribute, left column, several marketing areas, blog, banners, and tons of product displays. Spectacularly designed, Ultra Store is engineered to be a full-width responsive theme, so it takes advantage of your entire screen on any device (similar to Amazon).
